</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/iron-maiden">Iron Maiden</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ac-dc">AC/DC</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/judas-priest">Judas Priest</a>也将前来演出。</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/maynard-james-keenan-to-open-new-winemaking-facility-in-arizona-3492044">Tool&#39;s Maynard James Keenan to open new winemaking facility in Arizona</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
